
OWAMP/ -----> Meassurement tool related developed software (optimized for v3.4
         |
         +--> NTP-sync/ -----> Everything related to required NTP synchronization for OWAMP to work
         |                |
         |                +--> TUCAN_ntp.sh --> Boot script to open NTP port using iptables
         |                |
         |                +--> tacsa/ -----> Specific configurations/files for tacsa node
         |                |             |
         |                |             +--> ntp.conf --> NTP daemon configuration
         |                |
         |                +--> nurco/ -----> Specific configurations/files for nurco node
         |                              |
         |                              +--> ntp.conf --> NTP daemon configuration
         |
         +--> OWAMP-conf/ -----> Configuration files for OWAMP daemon
                            |
                            +--> TUCAN_owamp.sh --> Boot script to launch owamp server
                            |
                            +--> owamp --> Script to be placed at /etc/default, to set default options for owamp daemon
                            |
                            +--> owampd.conf --> Conf file to be placed at /etc/owampd, to set configuration option

motd --> Message Of The Day file, to customize ssh access to the node and present it to the user



